WEBVTT

00:00:28.180 --> 00:00:31.483
Ljudi često povezuju autizam

00:00:31.483 --> 00:00:34.156
sa sklonošću prema matematici i znanosti,

00:00:34.156 --> 00:00:35.955
i ničemu drugom, ali poznajem

00:00:35.955 --> 00:00:38.328
mnogo autističnih ljudi 
koji vole biti kreativni.

00:00:38.328 --> 00:00:40.770
Ali to je stereotip,

00:00:40.770 --> 00:00:42.626
i stereotipi o stvarima su često,

00:00:42.626 --> 00:00:45.888
ako ne i uvijek, pogrešni.

00:00:45.888 --> 00:00:48.306
Na primjer, mnogo ljudi pomisli autizam

00:00:48.306 --> 00:00:52.559
i odmah pomisli "Kišni čovjek".

00:00:52.559 --> 00:00:54.051
To je uobičajeno vjerovanje,

00:00:54.051 --> 00:00:57.346
da je svaka autistična osoba
Dustin Hoffman,

00:00:57.346 --> 00:01:00.349
ali to nije istina.